chart: c4
title: E-Commerce Platform

person Shopper | description: Browses products and places orders
person Admin | description: Manages inventory and fulfills orders

system Storefront | description: Customer-facing web store
  -Serves product pages to [HTTPS]-> Shopper
  -Processes charges via [HTTPS]-> Payments
  -Sends fulfillment requests to [HTTPS]-> Warehouse

system Payments | description: Stripe payment processing
  -Sends receipts to [Email]-> Shopper

system Warehouse | description: Inventory and shipping management
  ~Sends tracking updates to [Email]~> Shopper

system Back Office | description: Admin dashboard for order and inventory management
  -Provides management UI to [HTTPS]-> Admin
  -Queries stock levels from [HTTPS]-> Warehouse
  <-Syncs catalog data [JSON/HTTPS]-> Storefront
